 Redux

 "Store" -> application state. one place 
 where your state lives. single source of truth. 

 Services and Compoennts dispatch "Actions".

 "Actions" are sent to "Reducers" .
 where states are combined and the state is reduced.

 "Reducers" -> save the reduced state in the store. 

ngrx -> angualr redux
